headline: Phillips 66 (PSX) Valuation Check As Western Gateway Pipeline Open Season Progresses
summary: Why the Western Gateway Pipeline move matters for Phillips 66 stock Phillips 66 (PSX) and Kinder Morgan have kicked off a second open season for the proposed Western Gateway Pipeline after earlier shipper interest and commitments prompted them to offer remaining capacity. This step focuses on moving refined products from midcontinent refineries toward Phoenix and into California, with added access to Los Angeles through a joint tariff and reversed Kinder Morgan lines.
